Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:21.05,OPED,,0,0,0,,尔亦然也\N{\K304\fn DFGMaruGothic-SB\fs39\bord1\c&H0001cd&\3c&Hffffff&\pos(500,1050)}奴らも同じさ
